targets.query: SELECT count("exception") FROM "ALARMING" WHERE ("device" =~ /^$rtr$/) AND ALARM_TYPE=~/RED.*|TAIL.*/ and $timeFilter GROUP BY "ALARM_TYPE", "LINKNAME", queue_name, queue_id

select sum(cos_fw) from (SELECT "cos_forwarded_octets_rate"*8 as cos_fw FROM "COS" WHERE "device" =~ /^$rtr$/  and "if_name" =~ /^(et|xe|ge).*/  and if_unit='' and $timeFilter GROUP BY if_name,  "queue_id") group by queue_id
SELECT "exception" FROM "ALARMING" WHERE ("device" =~ /^$rtr$/) AND $timeFilter and ALARM_TYPE=~/RED.*|TAIL.*/ GROUP BY "ALARM_TYPE", "LINKNAME", queue_id, queue_name
SELECT mean("in_octets_rate")*8  FROM "COS" WHERE (device =~ /^$rtr$/ AND LINKNAME = '$ifname' and if_unit='') AND $timeFilter group by time($sample_interval)
SELECT mean("out_octets_rate")*8 FROM "COS" WHERE (device =~ /^$rtr$/ AND LINKNAME = '$ifname'  and if_unit='') AND $timeFilter group by time($sample_interval)
SELECT mean("in_pkts_rate")  FROM "COS" WHERE ("device" =~ /^$rtr$/ AND LINKNAME = '$ifname' and if_unit='') AND $timeFilter group by time($sample_interval)
SELECT mean("out_pkts_rate") FROM "COS" WHERE ("device" =~ /^$rtr$/ AND LINKNAME = '$ifname' and if_unit='') AND $timeFilter group by time($sample_interval)

SELECT mean("in_pkts_rate") - (mean("bcast_in_pkts_rate")+mean("mcast_in_pkts_rate"))  FROM "COS" WHERE ("device" =~ /^$rtr$/ AND LINKNAME = '$ifname' and if_unit='')AND $timeFilter group by time($sample_interval)

SELECT mean("out_pkts_rate") - (mean("bcast_out_pkts_rate")+mean("mcast_out_pkts_rate"))  FROM "COS" WHERE ("device" =~ /^$rtr$/ AND LINKNAME = '$ifname' and if_unit='') AND $timeFilter group by time($sample_interval)
SELECT mean("mcast_in_pkts_rate")  FROM "COS" WHERE ("device" =~ /^$rtr$/ AND LINKNAME = '$ifname' and if_unit='') AND $timeFilter group by time($sample_interval)
SELECT mean("mcast_out_pkts_rate")  FROM "COS" WHERE ("device" =~ /^$rtr$/ AND LINKNAME = '$ifname' and if_unit='') AND $timeFilter group by time($sample_interval)
SELECT mean("bcast_in_pkts_rate")  FROM "COS" WHERE ("device" =~ /^$rtr$/ AND LINKNAME = '$ifname' and if_unit='') AND $timeFilter group by time($sample_interval)
SELECT mean("bcast_out_pkts_rate") FROM "COS" WHERE ("device" =~ /^$rtr$/ AND LINKNAME = '$ifname' and if_unit='') AND $timeFilter group by time($sample_interval)

SELECT mean("cos_tail_dropped_packets_rate") FROM "COS" WHERE ("device" =~ /^$rtr$/ AND LINKNAME = '$ifname' and if_unit='') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($sample_interval), "queue_id"
SELECT last("cos_buffer_cur")/last("cos_buffer_size")*100 FROM "COS" WHERE ("device" =~ /^$rtr$/ AND LINKNAME = '$ifname' and if_unit='') and $timeFilter group by queue_id
SELECT("cos_buffer_cur")/("cos_buffer_size")*100 FROM "COS" WHERE ("device" =~ /^$rtr$/ AND LINKNAME = '$ifname' and if_unit='') and $timeFilter group by queue_id
SELECT "cos_forwarded_octets_rate"*8 FROM "COS" WHERE ("device" =~ /^$rtr$/ AND LINKNAME = '$ifname' and if_unit='')  and $timeFilter GROUP BY "queue_id"

SELECT mean("cos_forwarded_octets_rate")*8 FROM "COS" WHERE ("device" =~ /^$rtr$/ AND LINKNAME = '$ifname' and if_unit='')  and $timeFilter GROUP BY "queue_id", time($sample_interval)
SELECT mean("cos_queued_packets_rate") FROM "COS" WHERE ("device" =~ /^$rtr$/ AND LINKNAME = '$ifname' and if_unit='')  and $timeFilter GROUP BY "queue_id", time($sample_interval)
SELECT mean("cos_forwarded_packets_rate") FROM "COS" WHERE ("device" =~ /^$rtr$/ AND LINKNAME = '$ifname' and if_unit='') AND   $timeFilter GROUP BY "queue_id", time($sample_interval)
